<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN217-intro">tiṇai, potuviyal. tuṟai, kaiyaṟunilai. avaṉvaṭakkiruntāṉuḻaicceṉṟa picirāntaiyāraikkaṇṭu pottiyār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN217">
<l>niṉaikkuṅ kālai maruṭkai yuṭaittē</l>
<l>yeṉaiperuñ ciṟappiṉō ṭīṅkitu tuṇita</l>
<l>lataṉiṉu maruṭkai yuṭaittē piṟaṉāṭṭut</l>
<l>tōṟṟañ cāṉṟa cāṉṟōṉ pōṟṟi</l>
<l>yicaimara pāka naṭpuk kantāka</l>
<l>viṉaiyatōr kālai yīṅku varutal</l>
<l>varuva ṉeṉṟa kōṉatu perumaiyu</l>
<l>matupaḻu tiṉṟi vantava ṉaṟivum</l>
<l>viyattoṟum viyattoṟum viyappiṟan taṉṟē</l>
<l>yataṉāl, taṉkō liyaṅkāt tēyat tuṟaiyuñ</l>
<l>cāṉṟō ṉeñcuṟap peṟṟa toṉṟicai</l>
<l>yaṉṉōṉai yiḻantaviv vulaka</l>
<l>meṉṉā vatuko laḷiyatu tāṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">When thinking about [it] it is amazing, </l>
<l corresp="2">resolving on this here with ever so much superiority. </l>
<l corresp="3a-c">More than that is amazing </l>
<l corresp="6">[his] coming here at a time that is like this, </l>
<l corresp="5">being a pillar of friendship according to illustrious custom, </l>
<l corresp="3d-4">a worthy man paying respect who is worthy to appear in the land of another. </l>
<l corresp="7">The greatness of the king who said “he will come”, </l>
<l corresp="8">and the knowledge of the one who came without fault in that </l>
<l corresp="9">whenever wondering, whenever wondering it goes beyond wonder. </l>
<l>Therefore, the fame that is ancient, obtained so as to be experience in the heart </l>
<l corresp="10-11">by the worthy man who stayed in a land unmoved by his sceptre,  </l>
<l corresp="12">this world that has lost one like that, </l>
<l corresp="13">what will become of it? It is pitiable. </l> 
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
